I reminded her this morning

26
00:02:30,080 --> 00:02:32,920
to send her sister back
for a proper burial.

27
00:02:33,160 --> 00:02:34,120
Judging by the time now,

28
00:02:34,360 --> 00:02:36,360
she should be on her way.

29
00:02:38,240 --> 00:02:39,360
It's good to know that.

30
00:02:40,280 --> 00:02:41,960
There will be a fierce battle today.

31
00:02:45,360 --> 00:02:46,360
I don't have

32
00:02:49,280 --> 00:02:50,440
the strength

33
00:02:50,440 --> 00:02:51,480
to keep her safe.

34
00:02:52,640 --> 00:02:53,880
But that place

35
00:02:55,080 --> 00:02:55,880
is populated

36
00:02:56,640 --> 00:02:57,680
and full of secret tunnels.

37
00:02:58,560 --> 00:02:59,480
A complicated structure

38
00:03:01,240 --> 00:03:02,520
gives her a better chance of survival.

39
00:03:04,480 --> 00:03:05,720
She is alert.

40
00:03:07,680 --> 00:03:09,200
Not to mention Yan Xiu is with her.

41
00:03:09,840 --> 00:03:10,880
I believe

42
00:03:12,880 --> 00:03:14,960
she will survive this ordeal.

43
00:03:26,320 --> 00:03:27,000
Huaizhi.

44
00:03:28,560 --> 00:03:30,120
After I've attended
the imperial court meeting,

45
00:03:33,200 --> 00:03:34,800
take your retirement letter

46
00:03:37,440 --> 00:03:38,600
and leave this palace.

47
00:03:40,400 --> 00:03:41,560
Your Majesty!

48
00:03:43,440 --> 00:03:44,840
You've thought of an escape plan

49
00:03:44,840 --> 00:03:46,480
for all of us.

50
00:03:49,520 --> 00:03:52,440
But what will you do?

51
00:04:11,960 --> 00:04:13,480
There is no way for me to get out.

52
00:04:16,279 --> 00:04:18,120
There was never an escape plan for me.

53
00:04:26,680 --> 00:04:28,600
Your Majesty!

54
00:04:40,480 --> 00:04:42,200
Your Majesty.

55
00:04:46,600 --> 00:04:47,280
Yanzhi.

56
00:04:49,800 --> 00:04:50,680
Ruoling and I

57
00:04:52,760 --> 00:04:54,240
are here to see you off.

58
00:07:18,480 --> 00:07:19,640
You could have gone anywhere

59
00:07:19,640 --> 00:07:20,640
but this place.

60
00:07:20,920 --> 00:07:22,080
Hand over the posthumous edict.

61
00:07:22,320 --> 00:07:23,720
It's what's best for both of us.

62
00:07:39,360 --> 00:07:40,880
When did they install this contraption?

63
00:07:41,320 --> 00:07:42,280
Search for them!

64
00:07:42,720 --> 00:07:43,520
Yes!

65
00:07:48,600 --> 00:07:49,880
My sister foresaw this?

66
00:07:50,520 --> 00:07:51,120
Come with me.

67
00:07:51,480 --> 00:07:52,400
What about my sister?

68
00:07:52,520 --> 00:07:53,320
This place is safe.

69
00:07:53,520 --> 00:07:54,200
We'll come back for her

70
00:07:54,200 --> 00:07:55,000
when the job is done.

71
00:07:55,080 --> 00:07:55,680
Let's go.

72
00:08:09,560 --> 00:08:11,240
Why isn't Official Li here yet?

73
00:08:11,560 --> 00:08:12,440
I don't know.

74
00:08:12,800 --> 00:08:14,200
Before we parted ways yesterday,

75
00:08:14,320 --> 00:08:15,920
he promised he would be here today.

76
00:08:16,840 --> 00:08:20,280
Perhaps he's ill?

77
00:08:38,240 --> 00:08:39,039
You...

78
00:08:40,760 --> 00:08:43,080
How dare you drug me?

79
00:08:43,640 --> 00:08:45,160
One mistake

80
00:08:45,760 --> 00:08:47,080
will lead to countless more.

81
00:08:47,880 --> 00:08:48,560
Yes.

82
00:08:49,320 --> 00:08:51,000
I made a mistake back then.

83
00:08:51,200 --> 00:08:52,400
So this time,

84
00:08:52,520 --> 00:08:53,840
I won't make the same mistake again.

85
00:08:59,520 --> 00:09:00,240
What's wrong?

86
00:09:04,160 --> 00:09:04,960
It's here.

87
00:09:05,600 --> 00:09:06,400
My grandfather once

88
00:09:06,480 --> 00:09:07,760
took my sister and I to this place.

89
00:09:08,760 --> 00:09:09,640
The exit...

90
00:09:10,440 --> 00:09:11,360
The exit is over there.

91
00:09:11,920 --> 00:09:13,240
You've regained your memory.

92
00:09:16,640 --> 00:09:18,280
I will finish
what my grandfather started

93
00:09:18,800 --> 00:09:19,840
years ago.

94
00:09:46,400 --> 00:09:47,720
Your Majesty.

95
00:09:48,440 --> 00:09:51,120
Qiu Ziliang is full of
lies and deceptions.

96
00:09:51,400 --> 00:09:52,960
He has no regard for the laws,

97
00:09:53,360 --> 00:09:55,000
stashed weapons illegally,

98
00:09:55,440 --> 00:09:56,840
and hired his own private troops.

99
00:09:57,440 --> 00:09:58,840
He assassinated two princes,

100
00:09:58,960 --> 00:09:59,720
our Empress,

101
00:09:59,880 --> 00:10:00,800
and the four Ministers.

102
00:10:01,320 --> 00:10:02,960
He was removed from his titles,

103
00:10:03,280 --> 00:10:05,800
but the people are not satisfied
with his punishment.

104
00:10:06,560 --> 00:10:09,800
His crimes are beyond unspeakable!

105
00:10:11,480 --> 00:10:13,720
We request for Your Majesty
to pass wise judgment

106
00:10:13,720 --> 00:10:16,560
on the Qiu Ziliang and his ilk.

107
00:10:16,880 --> 00:10:18,920
Their punishment shall serve
as a reminder to the world.

108
00:10:24,560 --> 00:10:26,240
How should I proceed
with the investigation?

109
00:10:29,400 --> 00:10:32,560
This is the name list of those
in cahoot with Qiu Ziliang.

110
00:10:33,280 --> 00:10:34,880
Please have a look.

111
00:10:49,960 --> 00:10:52,060
(Liu Zhixuan, Liang Zhihuan)

112
00:10:56,170 --> 00:10:57,550
(Jiang Lin, Zhou Ping, Liu Ding)

113
00:11:04,840 --> 00:11:07,120
Qiu Ziliang surrendered yesterday,

114
00:11:08,280 --> 00:11:10,040
(Name list of Qiu Ziliang's followers)
and the name list is already presented to me.

115
00:11:13,120 --> 00:11:15,400
Your efficiency in handling the matter

116
00:11:15,920 --> 00:11:18,400
has impressed me deeply.

117
00:11:22,480 --> 00:11:25,800
We request for Your Majesty
to punish these villains

118
00:11:26,240 --> 00:11:28,320
and cleanse the Imperial Court
of their corruption.

119
00:11:32,720 --> 00:11:36,160
We request for Your Majesty
to punish these villains

120
00:11:36,360 --> 00:11:38,520
and cleanse the Imperial Court
of their corruption.

121
00:11:59,240 --> 00:12:00,000
There is nowhere to run now.

122
00:12:00,960 --> 00:12:01,880
Did Prince Guang

123
00:12:01,880 --> 00:12:02,840
send you after me?

124
00:12:04,800 --> 00:12:06,320
I still can't believe Prince Guang

125
00:12:06,560 --> 00:12:08,280
is actually an evil villain.

126
00:12:09,280 --> 00:12:10,040
A villain?

127
00:12:10,800 --> 00:12:12,400
He was never a villain.

128
00:12:12,920 --> 00:12:15,080
Qi Yan is the real problem here.

129
00:12:15,520 --> 00:12:17,760
You have no right to
slander His Majesty.

130
00:12:19,920 --> 00:12:20,760
You may open

131
00:12:20,800 --> 00:12:21,440
the scroll

132
00:12:21,560 --> 00:12:23,000
if you don't believe us.

133
00:12:23,160 --> 00:12:23,960
Find out who is

134
00:12:23,960 --> 00:12:25,600
the rightful heir to the throne.

135
00:12:28,920 --> 00:12:30,360
You want the posthumous edict.

136
00:12:30,640 --> 00:12:32,400
Then come and get it.

137
00:12:38,120 --> 00:12:39,400
I never like

138
00:12:39,400 --> 00:12:40,160
using violence.

139
00:12:40,360 --> 00:12:41,200
Not to mention

140
00:12:41,200 --> 00:12:42,520
you are Miss Yanzhi's little sister.

141
00:12:43,080 --> 00:12:44,320
Hand over the posthumous edict.

142
00:12:44,720 --> 00:12:45,560
I'll let you go.

143
00:12:45,720 --> 00:12:47,040
I promise you won't be hurt.

144
00:12:47,600 --> 00:12:48,720
It belongs to Prince Guang

145
00:12:48,720 --> 00:12:49,720
all along.

146
00:12:50,200 --> 00:12:51,840
The Late Emperor ordered Han Yue
to give it to

147
00:12:51,840 --> 00:12:52,520
your grandfather.

148
00:12:52,760 --> 00:12:54,240
He wanted your grandfather to
hand it to Prince Guang.

149
00:12:54,960 --> 00:12:55,720
How is it yours

150
00:12:55,800 --> 00:12:56,960
simply because you have it?

151
00:12:58,680 --> 00:13:01,560
Unfortunately, I am a stubborn person.

152
00:13:01,840 --> 00:13:03,560
It'd be great if I would hand it over.

153
00:13:03,840 --> 00:13:05,560
But since you plan to take it from me,

154
00:13:06,720 --> 00:13:07,960
not a chance.

155
00:13:14,160 --> 00:13:14,720
Your Majesty.

156
00:13:15,000 --> 00:13:16,200
After Qiu Ziliang's execution,

157
00:13:16,440 --> 00:13:18,000
the Shencai Army became leaderless.

158
00:13:18,080 --> 00:13:19,000
They are without a goal.

159
00:13:19,480 --> 00:13:20,360
We should select a new General-in-Chief

160
00:13:20,360 --> 00:13:21,720
as soon as possible.

161
00:13:22,120 --> 00:13:23,840
This is the name list of people

162
00:13:23,840 --> 00:13:24,640
we recommend.

163
00:13:24,960 --> 00:13:26,360
Please have a look.

164
00:13:35,040 --> 00:13:35,680
Your Majesty.

165
00:13:35,800 --> 00:13:36,640
This is the name list.

166
00:13:36,720 --> 00:13:37,840
Please have a look.

167
00:13:40,620 --> 00:13:43,630
(Han Ding)

168
00:13:48,490 --> 00:13:50,310
(Han Ding)

169
00:14:05,630 --> 00:14:06,670
(Name list of Shencai Army soldiers)

170
00:14:17,200 --> 00:14:18,680
Summon Hand Ding.

171
00:14:19,520 --> 00:14:22,960
His Majesty wishes to have a word
with Han Ding.

172
00:14:43,200 --> 00:14:43,720
I,

173
00:14:43,880 --> 00:14:44,560
Han Ding,

174
00:14:44,800 --> 00:14:46,040
greet Your Majesty.

175
00:14:46,960 --> 00:14:48,200
Do you wish

176
00:14:49,640 --> 00:14:51,720
to be the Shencai Army's
General-in-Chief?

177
00:15:03,280 --> 00:15:04,480
You leave me with no choice.

178
00:15:23,040 --> 00:15:24,160
My sister...

179
00:15:24,760 --> 00:15:26,240
I designed the secret chamber.

180
00:15:26,520 --> 00:15:27,560
I would surely know

181
00:15:27,560 --> 00:15:28,720
if you modified it.

182
00:15:31,280 --> 00:15:32,960
But I pity Miss Yanzhi.

183
00:15:33,600 --> 00:15:34,800
She is already dead,

184
00:15:35,200 --> 00:15:36,600
but she still can't have peace.

185
00:15:37,240 --> 00:15:38,440
What is it that you want?

186
00:15:39,080 --> 00:15:40,080
The same as always.

187
00:15:40,560 --> 00:15:41,560
Hand over the posthumous edict.

188
00:15:41,760 --> 00:15:42,360
Then I'll leave,

189
00:15:42,640 --> 00:15:43,480
and you can have her back.

190
00:15:47,280 --> 00:15:48,440
Don't make me do it.

191
00:15:53,480 --> 00:15:54,120
Ruoling.

192
00:15:58,200 --> 00:15:58,840
Fine.

193
00:16:05,400 --> 00:16:07,160
My sister comes before anything.

194
00:16:22,970 --> 00:16:25,690
(The heir shall be Prince Guang,
the thirteen prince.)

195
00:16:31,160 --> 00:16:31,720
Great.

196
00:16:32,000 --> 00:16:32,840
We're even now.

197
00:16:52,120 --> 00:16:52,720
Let's go.

198
00:17:08,440 --> 00:17:09,160
Sorry.

199
00:17:10,520 --> 00:17:11,720
I miscalculated.

200
00:17:13,240 --> 00:17:14,240
This isn't your fault.

201
00:17:14,920 --> 00:17:15,560
The posthumous edict

202
00:17:15,760 --> 00:17:17,200
was meant for Prince Guang anyway.

203
00:17:17,960 --> 00:17:19,520
His Majesty told me something

204
00:17:19,640 --> 00:17:21,119
I couldn't tell my sister.

205
00:17:21,480 --> 00:17:22,599
She didn't know,

206
00:17:22,839 --> 00:17:24,240
nor did Prince Guang.

207
00:17:26,640 --> 00:17:27,760
Take my sister with you

208
00:17:27,760 --> 00:17:28,359
and leave.

209
00:17:28,359 --> 00:17:28,960
What about you?

210
00:17:31,960 --> 00:17:32,480
Me?

211
00:17:33,280 --> 00:17:35,080
I must carry out my duty
as the Sword Bearer.

212
00:18:00,760 --> 00:18:01,320
Good.

213
00:18:03,480 --> 00:18:04,440
You have my permission.

214
00:18:08,040 --> 00:18:10,400
We are grateful for
Your Majesty's kindness.

215
00:18:17,320 --> 00:18:18,680
Is there anything else to report?

216
00:18:19,680 --> 00:18:21,640
Make your reports quick and subtle.

217
00:18:21,960 --> 00:18:22,880
Your Majesty,

218
00:18:23,280 --> 00:18:24,520
that's all for now.

219
00:18:25,000 --> 00:18:25,680
Great.

220
00:18:27,280 --> 00:18:28,360
Then dismiss.

221
00:18:29,160 --> 00:18:30,760
We thank Your Majesty.

222
00:18:31,040 --> 00:18:33,040
We shall be dismissed.

223
00:18:37,120 --> 00:18:38,440
Uncle, please stay.

224
00:19:47,040 --> 00:19:48,280
(Retirement letter)

225
00:20:02,040 --> 00:20:02,720
Uncle.

226
00:20:03,920 --> 00:20:04,640
Yu'er.

227
00:20:06,280 --> 00:20:07,440
I thought you had gone home.

228
00:20:08,240 --> 00:20:09,400
Why are you back again?

229
00:20:10,440 --> 00:20:11,040
Yu'er.

230
00:20:11,360 --> 00:20:12,960
It's not safe for you to be here.

231
00:20:13,120 --> 00:20:13,920
Come with me.

232
00:20:14,760 --> 00:20:15,280
Uncle.

233
00:20:15,560 --> 00:20:16,840
You know His Majesty needs help,

234
00:20:17,000 --> 00:20:18,320
are you going to abandon him?

235
00:20:21,680 --> 00:20:23,520
Do you think I would rather leave?

236
00:20:25,160 --> 00:20:27,320
His Majesty asked me to leave.

237
00:20:27,800 --> 00:20:28,720
He said

238
00:20:29,520 --> 00:20:30,880
I would only be a liability

239
00:20:31,720 --> 00:20:33,960
if I stayed.

240
00:20:34,760 --> 00:20:36,120
The master treated me with kindness,

241
00:20:36,520 --> 00:20:38,280
I shall repay him with my loyalty.

242
00:20:39,640 --> 00:20:40,200
Uncle.

243
00:20:41,080 --> 00:20:41,840
Stay.

244
00:20:42,840 --> 00:20:44,200
Let's help him together.

245
00:20:56,200 --> 00:20:57,600
Uncle, do you know

246
00:20:59,480 --> 00:21:01,200
why I asked you to stay?

247
00:21:07,810 --> 00:21:09,650
(Name list of Shencai Army soldiers)

248
00:21:10,960 --> 00:21:12,280
The names of the people

249
00:21:13,000 --> 00:21:15,200
I ordered Han Ding to assign to
the Shencai Army

250
00:21:15,200 --> 00:21:16,280
(Name list of Shencai Army soldiers)

251
00:21:16,280 --> 00:21:18,080
are on this list.

252
00:21:19,800 --> 00:21:20,400
But I have never

253
00:21:21,400 --> 00:21:22,000
promised them

254
00:21:22,000 --> 00:21:23,200
any benefit.

255
00:21:29,560 --> 00:21:31,280
Was it your doing?

256
00:21:37,440 --> 00:21:38,440
The Chess of Generals

257
00:21:39,160 --> 00:21:40,600
and Qiu Ziliang's confidants

258
00:21:41,680 --> 00:21:45,000
have been removed by Yanzhi.

259
00:21:45,800 --> 00:21:47,520
Yanzhi's only confidant

260
00:21:48,040 --> 00:21:49,600
was Yan Xiu.

261
00:21:50,400 --> 00:21:51,400
The rest of them

262
00:21:53,040 --> 00:21:54,240
were your men.

263
00:21:58,000 --> 00:21:59,120
As for the Violet Bureau,

264
00:22:02,000 --> 00:22:03,800
if Cheng Ruoyu doesn't return,

265
00:22:04,160 --> 00:22:07,920
it won't change the fact
that Madam Jade works for you.

266
