removing Qiu Ziliang

269
00:22:32,760 --> 00:22:34,560
would disperse this corruption

270
00:22:35,320 --> 00:22:36,800
and pave the way to a better future.

271
00:22:40,160 --> 00:22:41,360
But I never thought

272
00:22:45,720 --> 00:22:47,480
there was a man just as evil as he was.

273
00:23:05,800 --> 00:23:06,840
